    <item>
      <title>特朗普考虑挑战限制其支出权力的法律</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/white-house-eyes-fight-with-congress-courts-over-spending-power</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据彭博新闻社看到的一份文件显示，白宫正在考虑挑战一项已有 50 年历史的法律的合宪性，该法律限制了总统对联邦支出的控制、放松了公务员的解雇、限制了薪酬并控制了独立机构。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/white-house-eyes-fight-with-congress-courts-over-spending-power</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 20:33:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普签署莱肯·莱利法案，针对被指控犯罪的移民</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/trump-signs-laken-riley-act-targeting-migrants-accused-of-crimes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统唐纳德·特朗普周三签署了《莱肯·莱利法案》，旨在打击被指控犯罪的移民，特朗普称这是其政府承诺对无证移民和边境安全采取更严厉措施的核心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/trump-signs-laken-riley-act-targeting-migrants-accused-of-crimes</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 19:59:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
