      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/funding-trump-s-agenda-why-republicans-need-reconciliation-to-do-it</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 19:47:39 GMT</pubDate>
